![Architecture Diagram](./Screenshots/Screenshot%202025-10-24%20125249.png)

**Workflow:**
1. User uploads an image to the **S3 bucket**  
2. The S3 event triggers an **AWS Lambda function**  
3. Lambda calls **Amazon Rekognition** to detect labels  
4. Detected labels and metadata are uploaded to **Amazon OpenSearch** for indexing  
5. The indexed data can be queried or searched by users in real time  

